---

---

<section
  class="border-t scanlines-bg border-black/25 dark:border-white/20 max-w-full px-6 md:px-12 py-24 md:py-36"
  aria-labelledby="how-heading"
>
  <div
    class="scanlines-bg absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-12 ">
    <span
      class="font-jet text-xs flex  items-center  gap-x-7 sm:gap-x-10 uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-black dark:text-white/50"
    >
    <!-- +  -->
    <div class=" relative flex-col ">
      <div class=" my-9">
        <div class=" absolute w-px h-6 bg-black dark:bg-white/50" ></div>
        <div class=" w-px h-6 bg-black dark:bg-white/50 rotate-90"></div>
      </div>
      
    </div>

      <span class="text-black dark:text-white/50">Cómo funciona</span> 
    </span>
    <div
      class="flex-1 h-px max-w-6 sm:max-w-48 bg-black dark:bg-white/50"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
    </div>
    
  </div>

  <h2
    id="how-heading"
    class="font-departure text-3xl md:text-5xl uppercase text-black dark:text-white mb-16 max-w-3xl leading-tight"
  >
    tres sencillos pasos <br />
  </h2>

  <div class="steps-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="step-card py-10 md:pr-10" data-step="01">
      <div
        class="text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-5 font-departure text-primary"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        01
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3
          class="font-departure text-lg sm:text-2xl  uppercase text-black dark:text-white mb-3"
        >
          Elige tu juego
        </h3>
        <p
          class="font-jet text-xs sm:text-base text-black/60 dark:text-white/60 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Escribe el nombre del juego que vas a streamear o selecciona el modo
          Just Chatting. La IA genera frases específicas del contexto.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="step-card py-10 md:px-10" data-step="02">
      <div
        class="text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-5 font-departure text-primary"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        02
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3
          class="font-departure text-lg sm:text-2xl  uppercase text-black dark:text-white mb-3"
        >
          Activa el chat
        </h3>
        <p
          class="font-jet text-xs sm:text-base text-black/60 dark:text-white/60 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Lanza el stream simulado y el chat empieza a fluir. Usernames de
          colores, timestamps reales y emotes de 7TV incluidos.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="step-card py-10 md:pl-10" data-step="03">
      <div
        class="text-[3.5rem] leading-none mb-5 font-departure text-primary"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        03
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3
          class="font-departure text-lg sm:text-2xl uppercase text-black dark:text-white mb-3"
        >
          Practica y crece
        </h3>
        <p
          class="font-jet text-xs sm:text-base text-black/60 dark:text-white/60 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Ajusta la velocidad del chat. Responde. Acostúmbrate al ritmo. Cuando
          vayas en vivo, ya lo habrás hecho antes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Step card borders: top on mobile, left on desktop. Increased opacity for visibility. */
  .step-card {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .step-card {
      border-top-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .step-card {
      border-top: none;
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }
    .step-card:first-child {
      border-left: none;
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) and (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .step-card {
      border-left-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }
  }
</style>
